  position: absolute;
  top: -40px;
  left: 0;
  background: #000;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 8px;
  z-index: 1000;
}
```

4. **Best practice**: Place the skip link *before* all other focusable elements (e.g., in `page.html.twig`, just after `<body>`).

This ensures SC 2.4.1 (Bypass Blocks) is met: users can skip repetitive navigation (e.g., header, menus) to reach main content in one keypress.

